calculated_fields.Market Type:
// Created by Antoine Des Aulniers Favreau
// Updated on 10/13/2017 by Antoine Des Aulniers Favreau
// Current field is not being updated in RWH Market Dim. This is to make sure we do not have null values. This field replace some of the null values in RWH with the logical Market Title for each curve.
// Originally intended for IR curves. Also applied to Inflation curves and Vol. surfaces.

IF CONTAINS([Market Subtype],"Major Curve") THEN "Major IR"
ELSEIF CONTAINS([Market Subtype],"Minor") THEN "Minor IR"
elseif CONTAINS([Market Subtype],"Vol") then "Vol Surface"
ELSE [MARKET_TYPE]
END

